# Build context hygiene for the web image (context = repo root). Keep host node_modules / build
# artifacts out so pnpm reinstalls cleanly inside the image (correct platform binaries) and the
# context stays small. The Go API image uses its own apps/api/.dockerignore.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/out-tsc
**/.angular
.git
.github
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
# the web image does not need the Go backend sources
apps/api
